{
  "stem": "22883.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we went by foot from that place-- it's not far from Piaseczno, it's 16 kilometers from Warsaw-- up to almost-- Well, we went east, which means in the region of Lublin, in the center of Lublin district, where parents of my mother lived.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were-- apparently, we were running away from Germans, but when we came to [INAUDIBLE] and to that place in-- near-- near of Lublin, then we stopped.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we stayed there maybe two or three days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my father-- because we went in the company, apparently our neighbor and his son and his nephew was with us, and there was another neighbor.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So all together maybe six or seven people we were.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we-- we were walking eastward in-- in this group of seven people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And those fathers-- my father and the father of-- of my neighbor's colleague-- they went because they-- they went to the-- another village farther east.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And at when-- at the end of the day they came back and say, the Germans are there, so it means that we were already in between Germans troops.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So apparently in this location, which was located farther than-- than we were staying, the German was there already.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So there was no sense and no reason to go farther east.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So my father decided that now they-- they were going back from where we came.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Near Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went-- this-- this is an example that at this time I didn't do anything, act, on my own.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just fulfilling the orders of my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time I was 19 years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This-- my attitude, or my behavior was-- I was not yet in a-- in a state of rebelling parents.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was just obeying.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
